 * @name Simple Drag Box Zoom
 * @version 1.0.1.gl
 * @author: Nianwei Liu [nianwei at gmail dot com], contributions by Gary Little [gary at luxcentral.com]
 * @fileoverview This lib provides a very simple drag zoom. Holding shift key while drawing a box 
 * will zoom to the desired area. Only one line of code GMap2.enableDragZoom() is needed.
 */
